description: Retrieves the proxy configuration details for the specified Amazon Chime SDK Voice Connector.

nested_items.name: DefaultSessionExpiryMinutes
nested_items.description: The default number of minutes allowed for proxy sessions.

nested_items.name: Disabled
nested_items.description: When true, stops proxy sessions from being created on the specified Amazon Chime SDK Voice Connector.

nested_items.name: FallBackPhoneNumber
nested_items.description: The phone number to route calls to after a proxy session expires.

nested_items.name: PhoneNumberCountries
nested_items.description: The countries for proxy phone numbers to be selected from.
